 es\, creators and artists working on digital financial inclusion\; open wo
 rldwide. Apply via the Interledger fellowship page.\n\nOrganisation: Inter
 ledger Foundation\nLocation: Remote (worldwide)\nAward: USD 72\,000 person
 al stipend plus a USD 20\,000 project budget. No application fee.\nDuratio
 n: Fellowship term (project-based)\n\nMore: https://interledger.org/grant/
 fellowship
URL:https://interledger.org/grant/fellowship
LOCATION:Remote (worldwide)
